attributes.responseBody: [{"translatedText":"When restarting the computer, there is a high probability (7/10) that the system diagnostic light flashes: 2 orange, 7 white, and the screen is black. Press and hold the power button for 15 seconds to turn off the system diagnostic light, and then press the power button again to start the computer. The symptoms were confirmed after a clean install of 24H2. The employee who had been using the computer until then has left the company, so it is unclear whether the problem had been present for a long time. Currently, a clean install of Windows 11 Pro 23H2 has been performed, and the symptoms have not changed. The memory and LCD cable have been reseated, and no abnormalities have been found in the diagnostics.","sourceLanguage":"ja"}]
attributes.requestBody:
[パソコン再起動の際に高確率（7/10）で、システム診断ライト点滅：橙2白7となり画面が真っ黒。

電源ボタン長押し15秒でシステム診断ライトが消え、再度電源ボタンで起動できる。
24H2をクリーンインストールした後に症状を確認。それまで使用していた社員が退職したので以前から発症していたのかは不明。

5) Check all the boxes in the dialog box and select Delete my content.]
